1. *Činjenica* je da je sve što se dešava u našem životu imalo uticaj na našu budućnost. (The fact is that everything that happens in our life has had an impact on our future.)

2. Uvek je bilo teško prihvatiti realnu *činjenicu* da stvari ne idu onako kako bismo želeli. (It has always been difficult to accept the real fact that things are not going the way we want.)

3. U našem životu se dešavaju mnoga neočekivana dešavanja, a *činjenica* je da se moramo prilagoditi. (Many unexpected things happen in our life, and the fact is that we have to adapt.) 

4. Ono što se dešava u našem životu je *činjenica*, a sudbina je ono što činimo sa tim činjenicama. (What happens in our life is a fact, and destiny is what we do with those facts.) 

5. *Činjenica* je da postoje stvari koje ne možemo kontrolisati, ali to ne znači da ne možemo da doprinesemo promenama. (The fact is that there are things that we cannot control, but that doesn't mean we can't contribute to the changes.)